=== Vector Equality Tests ===
v1 == v2: true
v1 == v3: false
empty vector == []: true
[5.0] vector == [5.0] list: true
[5.0] vector == [6.0] list: false
vector == multi-element list: false
vector == non-numeric list: false
=== Matrix Equality Tests ===
m1 == m2: true
m1 == m3: false
empty matrix == []: true
[7.0] matrix == [5.0] list: false
[7.0] matrix == [7.0] list: true
matrix == multi-element list: false
=== Strict Context Tests (Inside Functions) ===
STRICT: vector == vector: true
STRICT: empty vector == []: true
STRICT: single vector == [5.0] list: true
STRICT: vector == multi-element list: false
STRICT: matrix == matrix: true
STRICT: empty matrix == []: true
STRICT: single matrix == [7.0] list: true
STRICT: matrix == multi-element list: false
